37 transmission of information relating to wagering pools or other similar information. (NRS
38 463.810, 463.820) Section 11 repeals the provisions of existing law governing global risk
39 management, and section 4 adds certain activities previously included in the definition of
40 “global risk management” to the definition of “information service.” Sections 9 and 10 of this
41 bill make conforming changes to remove references to global risk management in existing
42 law.
